overview: Two cops are dispatched to a junkyard and find more than they bargained for. Will they nab the offenders or be the ones who end up getting Nailed? See some very filthy men getting very dirty in Mustang tradition. Starring Ken Browning, Manuel Torres, Marco Paris, Jay Armstrong, Kyle Lewis, Marc Williams, Nick Marino, Brendan Davies, Danny Mann, and Johnny Wallace.
title: Nailed
